{
  "stem": "15962.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So humans had to pull wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the boys did that, because all able-bodied men were sent out to work on road-work or some heavy-- carrying stones or doing something for the-- constructing the camp or the war effort.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A few of us were selected to be messengers or to help in the support services.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For instance, the camp needed-- even though, minimally-- needed electricians to-- just to keep the barbed-wires electrified or to repair roofs or to distribute blankets, if there were any, or clothing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Collect clothing from those who arrived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Effect There was a huge-- well, huge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a group that was charged with helping in the gas chambers that had to push people into the gas chambers and then carry out the dead bodies and burn them and extract the gold teeth and cut the hair and use any conceivable raw material for the war effort.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were those who had to go to the ramp when the train arrived and sort out all the luggage, pick out-- throw toothbrushes on one pile and suitcases in another and false teeth and et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were many ways of employing people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a messenger for a department that supplied all sorts of utensils, either for the Germans or for the prisoners in better positions-- I don't know-- blankets, shoes, various stuff that was stored in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also carried messages from the various-- between the various camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to go through various check-points and salute the SS guards and give my number-- because names didn't exist, we were all just numbers-- and then proceed to my destination.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was this considered a better position than--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
